    governmentStanceEn: 'Sticks to the comprehensive income standard alongside flexible appeals.',
    oppositionStance: '建议用2020年CPF记录评估资格',
    oppositionStanceEn: 'Recommends using 2020 CPF records to assess eligibility.',
